“If I were to be face to face with my 11-year-old self, I would tell him, ‘Wear that turquoise, flamboyant sweatshirt. Be you, and as long as you’re living your life with kindness and you’re expressing yourself in a safe and positive way, then live it up.’”

You are a work of art, Nick (@nickbutlak), and we know your 11-year-old self is as proud of you as we are 🎨 Thanks for sharing your story and for being part of the Sephora family ❤️

Please follow the @trevorproject, the world’s largest suicide prevention and crisis intervention organization for LGBTQ+ young people, to learn more about how to help anyone overcoming a similar struggle.

From our friends at @caudalieus: Powered by grapes 🍇🍇 Did you know that the Vinoperfect collection was inspired by an ancient tradition in the French vineyard, where workers would spread grapevine sap all over their face and hands to erase sun damage? Caudalie harnessed the natural power of Viniferine, the grapevine sap, which is the star ingredient in our Vinoperfect collection! ✨

Our commitment to using clean & natural ingredients doesn’t stop there. We’re now certified Clean + Planet Positive at Sephora, meaning we’ve strengthened our commitment to the planet even further. All our products will feature recyclable, recycled or refillable packaging by the end of 2022 and we’re committed to sustainable sourcing and environmental giving, having planted over 8M trees with @1percentftp! 🌎 #CleanAtSephora ✨✨✨

From our friends at @tatcha: Did you know that as you sleep, your skin repairs itself? 🌙 It works hard all day, protecting you from environmental aggressors—but without enough rest, your skin barrier is depleted and allows pollutants to enter the skin. As moisture escapes, the proof appears in a range of irritations from redness to dry patches. It’s important to get enough rest each night—we recommend 8 hours!—so that your skin has time to recover and repair itself while you sleep.

Want to see visible change in your skin in just one night? 💙🌙 Get excited for NEW Indigo Overnight Repair, which helps boost your skin’s natural repair process so your skin can recover faster. 

Available at Sephora.
